        <abstract> 
<p>Provides evidence of self-sterility in <hi rend="italic">Gladiolus</hi>.</p>  
<p>Has observed three seed-leaves in some <hi rend="italic">Dianthus</hi> seedlings.</p>  
<p>Cannot cross, or grow from seed, <hi rend="italic">Dielytra spectabilis</hi>.</p> 
